---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Playground | Toby on Fitness Tech"
  description="IronVane का नवीनतम एपिसोड, फिटनेस गेम्स और ट्रेनिंग ऐप्स — सब एक जगह।"
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-neutral-950 text-white py-12 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          🎮 Playground
        </h1>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-lg">
          IronVane का नवीनतम एपिसोड, फिटनेस गेम्स और ट्रेनिंग ऐप्स — सब एक जगह।
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* ── IRONVANE ── */}
      <div class="mb-14">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500">⚔️ IronVane</h2>
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/@IronVaneStory"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-sm text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1"
          >
            YouTube चैनल →
          </a>
        </div>

        {/* Latest episode — highlighted */}
        <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border-2 border-blue-500/60 ring-1 ring-blue-500/20 overflow-hidden shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/20">
          <div class="p-5 pb-3 flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
            <div>
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-400">⭐ नवीनतम एपिसोड</span>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-1">CROSSFIRE — एपिसोड 13</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 mt-1">Ceryn's Road</p>
            </div>
            <span class="hidden sm:inline-flex text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-900/40 border border-green-500/40 text-green-300 whitespace-nowrap">🟢 नया</span>
          </div>
          <div class="px-5 pb-5">
            <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden w-full aspect-video bg-neutral-800">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Unlyz4mYDVA"
                class="w-full h-full"
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-sm">
              <a
                href="https://www.youtube.com/@IronVaneStory/videos"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors"
              >
                ▶ पूरी सीरीज़ YouTube पर देखें →
              </a>
              {/* Rumble — discontinued, linked, no embed/image */}
              <a
                href="https://rumble.com/c/IronVane"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-neutral-500 hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2"
                title="IronVane का Rumble चैनल अब अपडेट नहीं होता"
              >
                <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-neutral-700 text-neutral-500">बंद</span>
                Rumble चैनल →
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      {/* ── LIMINAL (discontinued) ── */}
      <div class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-4">🦊 LIMINAL</h2>
        <article class="bg-neutral-900/60 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-300">LIMINAL</h3>
            <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 text-neutral-400 whitespace-nowrap">⛔ बंद</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-4">समुद्र किनारे की सराय पर आधारित एक सुपरनैचुरल कॉमेडी सीरीज़। अब निर्माण में नहीं — रिलीज़ हुए एपिसोड YouTube पर उपलब्ध हैं।</p>
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vo_LQS1ubWc"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl border border-neutral-700 text-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors font-semibold"
          >
            ▶ YouTube पर देखें
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-4">🕹️ गेम्स</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-10">
        {/* MMA RPG */}
        <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 p-6 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">MMA RPG</h3>
            <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-900/40 border border-green-500/40 text-green-300">🟢 लाइव</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">टर्न-बेस्ड MMA फाइटिंग RPG। अपना फाइटर बनाइए, कॉम्बो में महारत हासिल कीजिए और रैंकिंग में ऊपर बढ़िए।</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">फाइटिंग</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">RPG</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">रणनीति</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://clawdassistant85-netizen.github.io/mma-rpg/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors font-semibold">
            ▶ अभी खेलें
          </a>
        </article>

        {/* Gridbound Realms */}
        <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 p-6 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Gridbound Realms</h3>
            <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-900/40 border border-green-500/40 text-green-300">🟢 लाइव</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">एक टैक्टिकल ग्रिड-आधारित रणनीति गेम। अपनी यूनिट्स को कमांड करें और राज्य पर विजय पाएं।</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">रणनीति</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">टैक्टिक्स</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">ग्रिड</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://clawdassistant85-netizen.github.io/gridbound-realms/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors font-semibold">
            ▶ अभी खेलें
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-4">📱 ऐप्स</h2>

      {/* 1 Peter Memory Trainer — featured, full width */}
      <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border-2 border-amber-500/50 ring-1 ring-amber-500/20 p-6 md:p-8 mb-6 shadow-lg shadow-amber-900/10">
        <div class="md:flex md:items-center md:justify-between md:gap-8">
          <div class="md:flex-1">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3 flex-wrap">
              <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white">1 Peter Memory Trainer</h3>
              <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-900/40 border border-amber-500/40 text-amber-300 whitespace-nowrap">🚧 निर्माणाधीन</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4 max-w-2xl">Alert Academy की तैयारी के लिए 1 पतरस (KJV) मेमोराइज़ेशन ट्रेनर — चंकिंग, विज़ुअल एंकर, इको ड्रिल्स, गायब होता टेक्स्ट, रेसिटेशन स्कोरिंग और स्पेस्ड रिव्यू।</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">धर्मग्रंथ</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">स्मरण</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">KJV</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 md:mt-0 md:flex-shrink-0">
            <a href="/hi/one-peter-memory/" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-amber-600 hover:bg-amber-500 transition-colors font-semibold text-lg">
              📖 ट्रेनर खोलें
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {/* BJJ Buddy */}
        <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 p-6 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">BJJ Buddy</h3>
            <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-900/40 border border-green-500/40 text-green-300">🟢 लाइव</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">अपने BJJ प्रशिक्षण को ट्रैक करें, रोल्स लॉग करें, प्रगति पर नज़र रखें और अपने ग्रैपलिंग गेम को बेहतर बनाएं।</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">BJJ</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">ट्रेनिंग लॉग</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">प्रगति</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://bjj-buddy.pages.dev/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-500 transition-colors font-semibold">
            🥋 खोलें
          </a>
        </article>

        {/* NutriTrack */}
        <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 p-6 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">NutriTrack</h3>
            <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-900/40 border border-green-500/40 text-green-300">🟢 लाइव</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">मुफ़्त न्यूट्रिशन ट्रैकिंग। अपने भोजन लॉग करें, मैक्रोज़ पूरे करें और अपने प्रशिक्षण को सही ईंधन दें।</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">न्यूट्रिशन</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Macros</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">मील लॉग</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://nutritrack.tobyonfitnesstech.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-500 transition-colors font-semibold">
            🥗 खोलें
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
